#. type: Title =
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Navigating this course"
msgstr "Parcourir ce cours"

#. type: Title ==
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:3
#, no-wrap
msgid "Content"
msgstr "Contenu"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:6
msgid "You can obtain the content of each module in a written format. You will find the transcript below each presentation. Click to expand the transcript."
msgstr "Vous pouvez obtenir le contenu de chaque module sous forme écrite. Vous trouverez la transcription sous chaque présentation. Cliquez pour développer la transcription."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "project-planning::transcript.png"
msgstr "project-planning::transcript.png"

#. type: Title ==
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Left navigation"
msgstr "Navigation de gauche"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:12
msgid "You will find the course navigation on the left side of the page. Some of the menu items expand/collapse."
msgstr "Vous trouverez la navigation du cours sur le côté gauche de la page. Certains éléments du menu se développent ou se réduisent."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "project-planning::left-nav.png"
msgstr "project-planning::left-nav.png"

#. type: Title ==
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "Right navigation"
msgstr "Navigation de droite"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:20
msgid "You will find individual page contents on the right side of the page."
msgstr "Vous trouverez le contenu de chaque page sur le côté droit de la page."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "project-planning::right-nav.png"
msgstr "project-planning::right-nav.png"

#. type: Title ==
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Bottom navigation"
msgstr "Barre de navigation inférieure"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:28
msgid "At the bottom of each page you will find forward and back buttons to move you through the content."
msgstr "Au bas de chaque page, vous trouverez des boutons \"avancer\" et \"reculer\" qui vous permettront de parcourir le contenu."

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "epn::course-bottom-nav.png"
msgstr "epn::course-bottom-nav.png"

#. type: Title ==
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Action icons"
msgstr "Icônes d'action"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:36
msgid "The course is comprised of modules. Each modules contains a series of actions for you to complete. This may include reading assignments, videos to watch, notes to take, and exercises to complete."
msgstr "Le cours est composé de modules. Chaque module contient une série d'actions à effectuer. Il peut s'agir de lectures à faire, de vidéos à regarder, de notes à prendre et d'exercices à compléter."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:38
msgid "Look for the following icons indicating you need to take action:"
msgstr "Recherchez les icônes suivantes qui indiquent que vous devez effectuer une action :"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:41
msgid "Reading assignments"
msgstr "Documents à lire"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:44
msgid "Watch a video"
msgstr "Regardez une vidéo"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:47
msgid "Check your understanding"
msgstr "Vérifiez votre compréhension"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:50
msgid "Complete an activity or exercise"
msgstr "Effectuez une activité ou un exercice"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/navigation.adoc:52
msgid "Discuss with your peers"
msgstr "Discutez avec vos pairs"

